title: Grateful Dead Live at Cal Expo on 1994-06-08
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, Walkin' Blues, Peggy-O, Me & My Uncle*-> Big River*, Stagger Lee, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Picasso Moon, Big Railroad Blues, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Space-> Samba In The Rain**-> All Along The Watchtower-> Standing On the Moon-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: I Fought the Law

* Weir on acoustic, **First Samba In The Rain Welnick-Hunter
